        <p> We just looked for a little something to eat and bought some water on the way back before we were in bed at 8:00 PM (02:00 AM German time) and wanted to watch another episode of our favorite series. We'll have to watch it again tonight, as we both fell asleep within seconds. </p>
        <p> What's next? </p>
        <p> We'll stay here in New York until December 25th, and then take the train to Washington D.C. On December 30th, we'll head back to New York. Here we'll stay again near JFK Airport and fly back to Germany on December 31st at 9:30 PM, landing in Hamburg around 2:10 PM. </p>
